Ahead of their 14th wedding anniversary, Obi Cubana has gushed over his wife, showering her with sweet words. The popular hotelier described her as the ‘sweetest thing that can never cause him diabetes’ among other adjectives. The father of five confessed getting marrying to his wife, Ebele Iyiegbu aka Lusheby, is one of the best decisions he’s made in life. Sharing a video of some thrilling moments with his wife and little son, the billionaire businessman wrote: “The Traditional wine carrying of this beautiful model-queen took place exactly 14yrs ago this day, in Obosi, Idemmili North LGA of Anambra State!!   Davido reportedly eyes Lori Harvey     I’m ready for an arranged marriage – Latsha…     Banky W wins Lagos PDP Reps primary rerun   “This is one of my life’s BEST decisions; getting married to this damsel!! “Ok, next week Tuesday 14th is our 14th wedding anniversary……the story continues then! @lush_eby ….nwanyi oma, mkpuru mma m, tomato jos m, udala usö m, azu cubana m, the sweetest thing that can NEVER cause me diabetes!!! I celebrate you everyday biko!!!”